data.title: Benito Caballero Garza
data.meta_description: Benito Caballero Garza is a Mexican politician and lawyer affiliated with the PRI. He currently serves as Deputy of the LXII Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing Nuevo León.
data.text:
Benito Caballero Garza (born 24 September 1965) is a Mexican politician and lawyer affiliated with the PRI. He currently serves as Deputy of the LXII Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing Nuevo León.[1]
